race.description: Book Your Christmas Party At Dtc Hcp
race.comment: PEACE BABY (4) kept coming but just failed to pick up the winner last start over 1100m at this track. Will derive benefit from that and with average luck can go one better. PATRIOTIC KING (1) was a big winner over 1000m and was heavily bet again back to this grade but was slow off. Lugs top weight, but he rates strongly and can threaten. SIGNOR BILL (5) got too far back last time but just missed in a CL2 prior and that reads well. Deserves another chance. MERCHANT DELIGHT (2) was plainer the latest but led and won a 58 prior. Maps well, and the 3kg claim brings him into it again. BEATIFICATION (7) has improved his last two and will be around the mark.
